title: Royals return to World Series, beat Blue Jays in ALCS Game 6
text:
> Top News Royals return to World Series, beat Blue Jays in ALCS Game 6 Kansas City Royals' Lorenzo Cain celebrates after scoring on a hit by Eric Hosmer past Toronto Blue Jays catcher Russell Martin during the eight inning in Game 6 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Friday, Oct. 23, 2015, in Kansas City, Mo. (AP Photo/Jae C. Hong)
